{"tid":418340,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺ps4 game好低質？","createTime":"2017-09-29T12:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T17:39:41.000Z","uid":135730,"like":8,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c83df5f7cc9a1cedd177fede6b650a23234946c4","tid":418340,"uid":135730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺ps4 game好低質？<br />\n人中之龍就悶到爆 故事又唔覺得吹奏到咁好睇 睇完都唔知邊個打邊個<br />\n打架場面整得唔好 唔夠爽<br />\n打個勒索哥洗錢打到2046 支線又唔撚好玩又無聊<br />\n真三國無雙仲on鳩 明明以前有個好正既立志模式 從士兵升到去大將 依加ps4版整個新人物出黎 整完都唔記得邊個打邊個 畫面就差唔多咁既水準 角色就出得越黎越冇真實感 例如劉備就變左個韓仔樣 動漫節這話要出果版仲on9 整個大地圖出黎  騎撚住隻馬鳩跑 去唔同checkpoints 打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  整撚埋濕鳩野    唔單止係冇黎進步 仲退撚曬步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前玩ps2 ps3 甚至係nds games可能畫面冇咁靚 但起碼個個都誠意之作 唔會悶到我玩一次就唔想玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e43a961d2458b165d207d56b6031eacdf8d9951","tid":418340,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:51:33.000Z","msg":"啱呀所以我玩緊ps1"},{"pid":"a7334ab742fd66b0f3fb8d2590f7751047faf77b","tid":418340,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"唔想玩就送部ps4俾我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6284060e8563aef83999499b5912c6e9568b04","tid":418340,"uid":15880,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"煲緊no man sky"},{"pid":"5c01101c53940cd9c4f748a1295b63f60c35b3fa","tid":418340,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"爆左gta5後就冇開過機了"},{"pid":"cb6446668971007a549e221d34025bd60c53680c","tid":418340,"uid":135730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想玩就送部ps4俾我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能我懷舊撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma